In the absence of the carrier for your country, choose the [global](#global) version of the carrier.\n\n**Note:** For the 2-character ISO-3166-1 country codes, see [Country and Region Codes](https://developer.paypal.com/docs/integration/direct/rest/country-codes/) .\n\nWhen you [add tracking information](https://developer.paypal.com/docs/api/tracking/v1#trackers-batch_post) or [update or cancel tracking information](https://developer.paypal.com/docs/api/tracking/v1#trackers_put) , you must choose a carrier.
